text: José María Rosillo (born 15 May 1952) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
